        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner North Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Heritage Character, Broad Buyer Pool</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Professionals, downsizers and investors competing for the same stock</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/lutwyche" style="color:#b98229;">Lutwyche</a>, <a href="/suburbs/gordon-park" style="color:#b98229;">Gordon Park</a>, <a href="/suburbs/fortitude-valley" style="color:#b98229;">Fortitude Valley</a>, <a href="/suburbs/ascot" style="color:#b98229;">Ascot</a>, <a href="/suburbs/bowen-hills" style="color:#b98229;">Bowen Hills</a>.</p>
