    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.75; color:rgba(25,24,23,0.72); margin-bottom:2rem;">Call Daniel directly for a no-obligation conversation about your property and what it could achieve in today's market.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      <a href="tel:+61412523821" style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b4610; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.02em;">0412 523 821</a>
